1
00:00:01,570 --> 00:00:04,590
<i>If I win this competition, please meet up with me once again.</i>

2
00:00:04,590 --> 00:00:06,450
<i>Don't come near her anymore. </i>

3
00:00:06,450 --> 00:00:08,710
<i>You aren't capable of making her happy.</i>

4
00:00:08,710 --> 00:00:11,450
<i>I can make her happier than you can.</i>

5
00:00:15,600 --> 00:00:17,820
<i>Won't you come with me to New York?</i>

6
00:00:17,820 --> 00:00:19,990
<i>I'll make you happy,</i>

7
00:00:19,990 --> 00:00:21,800
<i>I'll protect you!</i>

8
00:00:21,800 --> 00:00:23,260
<i>It was all a lie</i>

9
00:00:23,260 --> 00:00:24,900
<i>when I said I loved you, and</i>

10
00:00:24,900 --> 00:00:26,840
<i>even when I proposed to you.</i>

11
00:00:26,840 --> 00:00:30,630
<i>You're annoying.  Don't bother with me anymore.</i>

12
00:00:30,630 --> 00:00:33,600
<i>What's happened? What's happened??</i>

13
